import {
    Box, Grid, Icon, List, ListItem, ListItemText, SvgIcon,
    ListItemIcon, Paper, Stack, Typography, Divider, Chip, Avatar
} from "@material-ui/core";
import Masonry, { ResponsiveMasonry } from "react-responsive-masonry";
import avatar from "../images/profilePic.jpg";
import { red, indigo } from '@material-ui/core/colors';
import AI from "../images/artificial-intelligence.svg";
import Investing from "../images/profits.svg";

function AboutMe() {
    return (

        <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: 're', width: 1, maxWidth: '54rem', alignSelf: 'center', overflow: 'auto' }}>
            <ResponsiveMasonry
                columnsCountBreakPoints={{ 350: 1, 600: 2, 750: 2, 900: 2 }}>
                <Masonry gutter='0.5rem' style={{ padding: '0.4rem' }}>
                    {/* profile card  */}
                    <Paper  sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem' }}>
                        <Grid container>
                            <Grid item flexGrow='1'>
                                <Box sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', backgroundColor: 're' }}>
                                    <Box component='img' width='9rem' src={avatar} sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem', border: '1px solid #d3d3d3', p: 10 / 12 }} />
                                </Box>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item flexGrow='0.6'>
                                <Box sx={{ width: '100%', height: '12rem', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center', backgroundColor: 'blu', gap: 1.5 }}>
                                    <Typography sx={{ fontSize: '1.5rem', fontFamily: 'sans-serif', fontWeight: '600', color: 'success.dark' }}>
                                        Brian Ojoh Mile
                                    </Typography>
                                    <Typography sx={{ fontWeight: '600', fontSize: '1.1rem' }}>Full Stack Developer</Typography>
                                    <Typography sx={{ fontWeight: '600', fontSize: '1.1rem' }}>Laurel, MD</Typography>
                                    <Stack direction='row' spacing={1} sx={{ border: 2, p: 1, borderRadius: '1rem', color: 'error.main' }}>
                                        <Icon component='a' baseClassName='fab' className='fa-github' sx={{ fontSize: '1.8rem', color: 'error.main' }}
                                            href='https://github.com/Feidorian' target='_blank' />
                                        <Icon baseClassName='fab' className='fa-linkedin' sx={{ fontSize: '1.8rem', color: 'error.main' }}
                                            component='a' href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brian-ojoh-mile-a5a7b9154/" target='_blank' />
                                    </Stack>
                                </Box>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Paper>

                    {/* general info card  */}
                    <Paper  sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem' }}>
                        <List sx={{ px: '0.7rem' }}>
                            {/* name */}
                            <ListItem disableGutters>
                                <ListItemIcon >
                                    <Icon sx={{ color: indigo[900] }}>face</Icon>
                                </ListItemIcon>
                                <ListItemText >
                                    <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color={indigo[900]} mx={-3}>Full Name</Typography>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <Typography sx={{ whiteSpace: 'normal', textAlign: 'center' }}>Brian T. Ojoh Mile</Typography>
                            </ListItem>
                            <Divider sx={{ width: '94%', mx: 'auto' }} />
                            {/* phone number  */}
                            <ListItem disableGutters>
                                <ListItemIcon>
                                    <Icon sx={{ color: indigo[900] }}>smartphone</Icon>
                                </ListItemIcon>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color={indigo[900]} mx={-3}>Mobile</Typography>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <Typography>(240) 524-0631</Typography>
                            </ListItem>
                            <Divider sx={{ width: '94%', mx: 'auto' }} />
                            {/* email  */}
                            <ListItem disableGutters>
                                <ListItemIcon>
                                    <Icon sx={{ color: indigo[900] }}>email</Icon>
                                </ListItemIcon>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color={indigo[900]} mx={-3}>Email</Typography>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <Typography sx={{ whiteSpace: 'normal', textAlign: 'center' }}>contact@feidorian.dev</Typography>
                            </ListItem>
                            <Divider sx={{ width: '94%', mx: 'auto' }} />
                            {/* degree */}
                            <ListItem disableGutters>
                                <ListItemIcon>
                                    <Icon sx={{ color: indigo[900] }}>receipt</Icon>
                                </ListItemIcon>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color={indigo[900]} mx={-3}>Degree</Typography>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <Typography sx={{ whiteSpace: 'normal', textAlign: 'center' }}>BS Computer Science</Typography>
                            </ListItem>
                            <Divider sx={{ width: '94%', mx: 'auto' }} />
                            {/* undergraduate */}
                            <ListItem disableGutters>
                                <ListItemIcon>
                                    <Icon sx={{ color: indigo[900] }}>school</Icon>
                                </ListItemIcon>
                                <ListItemText>
                                    <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color={indigo[900]} mx={-3}>College</Typography>
                                </ListItemText>
                                <Typography sx={{ whiteSpace: 'normal', textAlign: 'center' }}>University of Maryland, College Park</Typography>
                            </ListItem>
                        </List>
                    </Paper>

                    {/* personal quote card  */}
                    <Paper  sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem', backgroundColor: indigo[900], color: 'white' }}>
                        <Typography sx={{ textAlign: 'center', p: '0.4rem', fontStyle: 'italic' }}>
                            "Programming to me is the multitudes of points where imagination meets reality. The multitude
                            of points when I gaze over fragments of code and Exclaim to
                            myself: I IMAGINED that, I BUILT that, and I made it USEFUL."
                        </Typography>
                    </Paper>

                    <Paper />
                    <Paper component={Stack} spacing={1} alignItems='center' p={1} sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem', backgroundColor: 'white' }}>
                        <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={600} color={indigo[900]}>Background</Typography>
                        <Typography textAlign='center' fontWeight={500}>
                            I am a Full Stack Developer with a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science from the University of Maryland College Park.
                            I Specialize in Web Development, with proficiency in libraries such as React, Bootstrap, Tailwind & Material UI.
                            I Subspecialize in mobile app development (particularly android App Development with Kotlin).
                            I also have some DataScience Experience: Jupyter, Docker, Data Visualization(seaborn, matplotlib),
                            Data Management(panda, sql, csv, json, html tables, etc), & Data Modeling(machine learning models).
                        </Typography>
                    </Paper>

                    <Paper component={Stack} alignItems='center' p={1} sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem', backgroundColor: 'white' }}>
                        <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color='#1A237E'>Interests</Typography>
                        <Grid container justifyContent='center' spacing={1} flexWrap='wrap'>
                            <Grid item>
                                <Chip component={Grid} item color='primary' sx={{ fontSize: '1rem', color:'#1A237E', borderColor:'#1A237E' }}
                                    icon={<Icon baseClassName='fas' color='success' className='fa-robot' sx={{ width: 'fit-content', fontSize: '1.2rem' }} />}
                                    label='Machine Learning' variant='outlined' />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item>
                                <Chip component={Grid} item sx={{ fontSize: '1rem', color:'#1A237E', borderColor:'#1A237E' }}
                                    icon={<Icon component='img' src={AI} />}
                                    label='Artificial Intelligence' variant='outlined' />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item>
                                <Chip component={Grid} item color='primary' sx={{ fontSize: '1rem', color:'#1A237E', borderColor:'#1A237E'  }}
                                    icon={<Icon baseClassName='fas' color='success' className='fa-robot' sx={{ width: 'fit-content', fontSize: '1.2rem' }} />}
                                    label='Machine Learning' variant='outlined' />
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Paper>
                    <Paper />
                    <Paper component={Stack} alignItems='center' p={1} elevation={2} sx={{ borderRadius: '0.5rem', backgroundColor: 'white' }}>
                        <Typography fontSize='1.3rem' fontWeight={500} color={red[900]}>Hobbies</Typography>
                        <Grid container justifyContent='center' spacing={1} flexWrap='wrap'>
                            <Grid item>
                                <Chip item color='error' sx={{ fontSize: '1rem' }}
                                    icon={<Icon baseClassName='fas' className='fa-chart-line' sx={{ width: 'fit-content', fontSize: '1.2rem', color:'#D50000' }} />}
                                    label='Investing' variant='outlined' />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item>
                                <Chip component={Grid} item color='primary' sx={{ fontSize: '1rem' }}
                                    icon={<Icon baseClassName='fas' color='success' className='fa-robot' sx={{ width: 'fit-content', fontSize: '1.2rem' }} />}
                                    label='Machine Learning' variant='outlined' />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item>
                                <Chip component={Grid} item color='primary' sx={{ fontSize: '1rem' }}
                                    icon={<Icon baseClassName='fas' color='success' className='fa-robot' sx={{ width: 'fit-content', fontSize: '1.2rem' }} />}
                                    label='Machine Learning' variant='outlined' />
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Paper>

                </Masonry>
            </ResponsiveMasonry>
        </Box>

    )
}

export default AboutMe;
